query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM protocolChunks) as total_protocols,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT protocolNumber) FROM protocolChunks) as unique_protocols,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM counties) as total_counties;
